Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is  good thing. I believe it is good practice for students and young adults to understand the basics of living with a companion or in a social setting with many fellow adolescents. Also it teaches studens responsibility and how to adapt to a new mosy likely unfamiliar environment. 